<FlowDefinition xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <activeVersionNumber>1</activeVersionNumber>
    <description>Whenever a new Lead record is inserted in Salesforce, we need a new Case to be created. This new case should be associated with the newly created Lead as a child record. Also, we need to create a new Task related to this newly created Case.

New Lead Created by User/System --&gt; Flow Trigger Is Fired Automatically after Lead is Saved --&gt; Fetch the Record of new Lead in Flow --&gt; Create Child Case for this Lead --&gt; Create a new Task for this Case</description>
    <masterLabel>After Save(Creation On Lead Record)</masterLabel>
</FlowDefinition>
